      html: "<h2>1. What are cookies?</h2>\n<p>MUA Match uses cookies and similar technologies on its website and platform. Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit our website. These technologies help us ensure that the platform works properly, improve user experience, analyse usage, maintain security, and provide relevant marketing.</p>\n<p>Cookies do not damage your device and generally do not contain viruses.</p>\n<h2>2. Which cookies does MUA Match use?</h2>\n<h3>Functional cookies</h3>\n<p>These cookies are necessary for the proper functioning of the MUA Match website and platform. They enable essential functions such as account access, authentication, security, preferences, and platform functionality.</p>\n<p>These cookies may be placed without consent where they are strictly necessary for providing the service requested by the user.</p>\n<h3>Analytical and performance cookies</h3>\n<p>MUA Match uses analytical and performance tools to understand how visitors use the platform and to improve functionality and performance.</p>\n<p>MUA Match may use:</p>\n<ol><li>Google Analytics: to collect anonymous or aggregated information about website usage, visitor behaviour, and performance.</li><li>Firebase Analytics: to analyse usage of the MUA Match application, monitor user interactions, and improve app functionality.</li><li>Sentry: to monitor technical errors, crashes, and platform performance in order to maintain reliability and security.</li></ol>\n<p>Where required by law, these cookies and technologies are only activated after obtaining your consent.</p>\n<h3>Payment-related technologies</h3>\n<p>MUA Match uses <strong>Stripe</strong> for payment processing. Stripe may use cookies or similar technologies necessary for secure payment processing, fraud prevention, authentication, and payment security.</p>\n<p>Stripe may process certain information according to its own privacy and cookie policies.</p>\n<h3>Marketing cookies</h3>\n<p>MUA Match uses marketing technologies to measure advertising performance and improve marketing activities.</p>\n<p>MUA Match may use:</p>\n<ol><li>Meta Pixel: to measure the effectiveness of advertisements on platforms such as Facebook and Instagram, understand visitor behaviour, and provide more relevant advertising.</li></ol>\n<p>Marketing cookies are only placed after your consent.</p>\n<h2>3. Cookie preferences</h2>\n<p>When you visit the MUA Match website, you can choose which categories of cookies you allow through the cookie banner.</p>\n<p>You can accept, reject, or adjust your cookie preferences at any time. You may also delete cookies through your browser settings.</p>\n<p>Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect the availability or functionality of parts of the platform.</p>\n<h2>4. Third-party cookies</h2>\n<p>Some cookies and similar technologies are placed by third-party service providers used by MUA Match. These parties may process information according to their own privacy policies.</p>\n<p>Third parties currently used by MUA Match may include:</p>\n<ul><li>Google Analytics</li><li>Firebase</li><li>Sentry</li><li>Stripe</li><li>Meta</li></ul>\n<h2>5. Changes to this Cookie Policy</h2>\n<p>MUA Match reserves the right to update this Cookie Policy when changes are made to the cookies and technologies used on the platform or when legal requirements change.</p>\n<p>The most recent version will always be available on the MUA Match website.</p>\n<h2>6. Contact</h2>\n<p>If you have questions about this Cookie Policy or the use of cookies by MUA Match, you can contact MUA Match through the contact details provided on the website.</p>",
